{"tid":1541743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實一開始講訴求已經好錯","createTime":"2019-09-04T15:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T16:01:24.000Z","uid":232275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"631263b74c73dce68ed4b25f49ec2cc76693a210","tid":1541743,"uid":232275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:53:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">雖然依家我地嗌緊五大訴求，缺一不可，<br />\n<br />\n但希望香港人唔好忘記，權力永遠係屬於人民，人民根本唔需要向政府哀求，亦根本唔需要理會呢個非民選政府既回應，<br />\n<br />\n香港人必須要知道我地先係權力既主宰，我地必須要有奪回主權既覺醒。<br />\n<br />\n香港人先係呢塊土地既主人，而唔係呢區區幾百人既港共政府，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">願榮光和主權永遠歸於香港人民！</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n</span></div>"},{"pid":"5af6113346b4fa965723ed5c2f9ad54f42b4a405","tid":1541743,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:54:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"894b52788ae127fc092bcdfbb9069aed7ae2c1f3","tid":1541743,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:01:24.000Z","msg":"其實宜家 五大訴求，一個都冇達成.<br />\n希望英文宣強調番宜家只係<span style=\"color: red;\">動議撤回</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">motion to withdraw</span> only<br />\n<br />\n送中未撤回嫁, 只係 . 動 . 議 . 撤回 [唔好比林鄭呃左, 宜家仲係0個訴求達成]<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1541711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1541711</a>"}]}